{"type":"message","id":"4b7eb1f8","parentId":"366647dd","timestamp":"2026-07-13T06:03:47.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're right. That's a miss on my end.\n\nSame image = looks automated, hurts engagement, weakens the brand. Each post deserves its own visual.\n\nGoing forward:\n- **Every post gets a unique image** generated specifically for that topic\n- I'll use the `image-gen` skill to create LinkedIn-ready visuals (16:9, saved to your images folder)\n- No more recycling the same generic image\n\nFor the next batch of posts, I'll generate fresh images for each one before publishing. Want me to set up a quick test now so you can see the variety?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783922617742,"responseId":"u39Uarb1I_qAn9kP18C2qA8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdb50fd5-1801-4563-ace3-64708f449d84","parentId":"4b7eb1f8","timestamp":"2026-07-13T06:03:49.299Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You're right. That's a miss on my end.\n\nSame image = looks automated, hurts engagement, weakens the brand. Each post deserves its own visual.\n\nGoing forward:\n- **Every post gets a unique image** generated specifically for that topic\n- I'll use the `image-gen` skill to create LinkedIn-ready visuals (16:9, saved to your images folder)\n- No more recycling the same generic image\n\nFor the next batch of posts, I'll generate fresh images for each one before publishing. Want me to set up a quick test now so you can see the variety?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783922629242,"openclawDeliveryMirror":{"kind":"channel-final","sourceMessageId":"telegram-final:agent:main:main:264468965:571:0"},"idempotencyKey":"telegram-final:agent:main:main:264468965:571:0"}}
