{"type":"message","id":"16a71ca1-51d2-40ca-93d3-8ac2a259e6ff","parentId":"2066d261","timestamp":"2026-07-13T07:44:51.043Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Andrii — you're showing up. 5 posts this week. That's the work.\n\nBut you set the bar at 2-3/day. You're at ~1/day. Close, but not the pace that wins.\n\nHere's what's next from your calendar:\n\n**Trend Proposals — 10 days stale**\nYour last trend research was July 3. You've got 4 proposed posts waiting:\n\n1. \"Your AI agent went down last week. You didn't notice.\" (Claude Fable outage)\n2. \"The best AI stack isn't one model. It's zero bloat.\" (Trunk Tools)\n3. \"Inference costs are about to collapse.\" (DeepSeek DSpark)\n4. \"Morgan Stanley's best AI win? Making agents LESS autonomous.\"\n\nKnock one out now?"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783928691006,"idempotencyKey":"7e96c090-b078-4a59-a1ee-d035170574d0:message-tool:jNq_KTq3vQc2LPqt6KcZShIv:call_a44c3facd25c41d292d9bc5e"}}
