{"type":"message","id":"6aa5a019","parentId":"381fd456","timestamp":"2026-07-15T00:14:15.012Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8e6f1d0641944f03bef85374","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ALREADY_SENT=false\nUID=264468965\nNAME=Andrii Bidochko\nTODAY=2026-07-15\nPOSTS_TODAY=0\nHAS_TOKEN=***\n---PILLARS---\n## Content Pillars\n\n1. Business & entrepreneurship insights\n2. Technology & AI innovations\n3. Personal development & mindset\n\n## Company / Product Context\n\n- **Company:** UBOS (ubos.tech)\n- **What it does:** AI Agent Orchestration Platform - build, host, and manage AI Agents in minutes using open-source tools (Langchain, CrewAI, Autogen, Vertex AI), 100+ LLM models, one-click cloud/on-premise deployment\n- **Key differentiators:** No vendor lock-in (open-source, multi-cloud), unlimited agents as microservices, works with any LLM including self-hosted (Llama, Deepseek)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":80,"aggregated":"ALREADY_SENT=false\nUID=264468965\nNAME=Andrii Bidochko\nTODAY=2026-07-15\nPOSTS_TODAY=0\nHAS_TOKEN=***\n---PILLARS---\n## Content Pillars\n\n1. Business & entrepreneurship insights\n2. Technology & AI innovations\n3. Personal development & mindset\n\n## Company / Product Context\n\n- **Company:** UBOS (ubos.tech)\n- **What it does:** AI Agent Orchestration Platform - build, host, and manage AI Agents in minutes using open-source tools (Langchain, CrewAI, Autogen, Vertex AI), 100+ LLM models, one-click cloud/on-premise deployment\n- **Key differentiators:** No vendor lock-in (open-source, multi-cloud), unlimited agents as microservices, works with any LLM including self-hosted (Llama, Deepseek)","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1784074455004}}
