{"type":"message","id":"6af8d7e1","parentId":"71c82219","timestamp":"2026-07-16T00:14:06.141Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7dc6587a20d34709bf0a2b1f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"UID=\"264468965\"\nBASE=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID\"\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nPENDING_DIR=\"$BASE/pending\"\n\n# OAuth check\nACCESS_TOKEN=*** -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].access_token // empty' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\nDISPLAY_NAME=$(jq -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].display_name // \"there\"' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\n\n# Check if brief already sent today\nBRIEF_FLAG=\"$PENDING_DIR/.brief-sent-$TODAY\"\n[ -f \"$BRIEF_FLAG\" ] && echo \"ALREADY_SENT=true\" || echo \"ALREADY_SENT=false\"\n\n# Load brand voice pillars\nif [ -f \"$BASE/profile.md\" ]; then\n  PILLARS=$(grep -A 10 \"Content Pillars\" \"$BASE/profile.md\" | head -12)\nfi\n\n# Check posts already published today\nPOSTS_TODAY=$(find \"$BASE/posts/\" -name \"${TODAY}-*.md\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\n\nmkdir -p \"$PENDING_DIR\"\n\necho \"UID=$UID\"\necho \"NAME=$DISPLAY_NAME\"\necho \"TODAY=$TODAY\"\necho \"POSTS_TODAY=$POSTS_TODAY\"\n[ -n \"$ACCESS_TOKEN\" ] && echo \"HAS_TOKEN=***\" || echo \"HAS_TOKEN=***\"\necho \"---PILLARS---\"\necho \"$PILLARS\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"UID=\\\"264468965\\\"\\nBASE=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID\\\"\\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\\nPENDING_DIR=\\\"$BASE/pending\\\"\\n\\n# OAuth check\\nACCESS_TOKEN=$(jq -r --arg u \\\"$UID\\\" '.[$u].access_token // empty' \\\"$TOKEN_STORE\\\" 2>/dev/null)\\nDISPLAY_NAME=$(jq -r --arg u \\\"$UID\\\" '.[$u].display_name // \\\"there\\\"' \\\"$TOKEN_STORE\\\" 2>/dev/null)\\n\\n# Check if brief already sent today\\nBRIEF_FLAG=\\\"$PENDING_DIR/.brief-sent-$TODAY\\\"\\n[ -f \\\"$BRIEF_FLAG\\\" ] && echo \\\"ALREADY_SENT=true\\\" || echo \\\"ALREADY_SENT=false\\\"\\n\\n# Load brand voice pillars\\nif [ -f \\\"$BASE/profile.md\\\" ]; then\\n  PILLARS=$(grep -A 10 \\\"Content Pillars\\\" \\\"$BASE/profile.md\\\" | head -12)\\nfi\\n\\n# Check posts already published today\\nPOSTS_TODAY=$(find \\\"$BASE/posts/\\\" -name \\\"${TODAY}-*.md\\\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\\n\\nmkdir -p \\\"$PENDING_DIR\\\"\\n\\necho \\\"UID=$UID\\\"\\necho \\\"NAME=$DISPLAY_NAME\\\"\\necho \\\"TODAY=$TODAY\\\"\\necho \\\"POSTS_TODAY=$POSTS_TODAY\\\"\\n[ -n \\\"$ACCESS_TOKEN\\\" ] && echo \\\"HAS_TOKEN=***\\\" || echo \\\"HAS_TOKEN=***\\\"\\necho \\\"---PILLARS---\\\"\\necho \\\"$PILLARS\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1784160829903,"responseId":"4e8d669e-9393-4a48-a66b-89b571a12c9f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec7a5bb9","parentId":"6af8d7e1","timestamp":"2026-07-16T00:14:06.406Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7dc6587a20d34709bf0a2b1f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ALREADY_SENT=false\nUID=264468965\nNAME=Andrii Bidochko\nTODAY=2026-07-16\nPOSTS_TODAY=0\nHAS_TOKEN=***\n---PILLARS---\n## Content Pillars\n\n1. Business & entrepreneurship insights\n2. Technology & AI innovations\n3. Personal development & mindset\n\n## Company / Product Context\n\n- **Company:** UBOS (ubos.tech)\n- **What it does:** AI Agent Orchestration Platform - build, host, and manage AI Agents in minutes using open-source tools (Langchain, CrewAI, Autogen, Vertex AI), 100+ LLM models, one-click cloud/on-premise deployment\n- **Key differentiators:** No vendor lock-in (open-source, multi-cloud), unlimited agents as microservices, works with any LLM including self-hosted (Llama, Deepseek)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":71,"aggregated":"ALREADY_SENT=false\nUID=264468965\nNAME=Andrii Bidochko\nTODAY=2026-07-16\nPOSTS_TODAY=0\nHAS_TOKEN=***\n---PILLARS---\n## Content Pillars\n\n1. Business & entrepreneurship insights\n2. Technology & AI innovations\n3. Personal development & mindset\n\n## Company / Product Context\n\n- **Company:** UBOS (ubos.tech)\n- **What it does:** AI Agent Orchestration Platform - build, host, and manage AI Agents in minutes using open-source tools (Langchain, CrewAI, Autogen, Vertex AI), 100+ LLM models, one-click cloud/on-premise deployment\n- **Key differentiators:** No vendor lock-in (open-source, multi-cloud), unlimited agents as microservices, works with any LLM including self-hosted (Llama, Deepseek)","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1784160846399}}
